#. そうだ…あの床板って、
#. <CLT=cltSTRONG>シーソー<CLT=cltNORMAL>になっていたんじゃないかな？
msgctxt "0000 | c03_225_000 | C000_Saiha"
msgid ""
"That's right... The floorboard might have\n"
"been used as a <CLT=cltSTRONG>seesaw<CLT=cltNORMAL>."
msgstr ""

#. んあっ？　シーソーじゃと？
msgctxt "0001 | c03_225_000 | C009_Yumen"
msgid "Nyeh? A seesaw?"
msgstr ""

#. 横木が切られていたのは、
#. 床板の端の部分だったんだ。
msgctxt "0002 | c03_225_000 | C000_Saiha"
msgid ""
"The crosspiece at one end of the\n"
"floorboard had been cut off."
msgstr ""

#. そして、床板を支えていた他の２本の横木は、
#. 茶柱さんの真下と床板の中央付近にあった。
msgctxt "0003 | c03_225_000 | C000_Saiha"
msgid ""
"The other two crosspieces holding up\n"
"that board were close to the cage."
msgstr ""

#. この状態で、横木がなくなった床板の端を
#. 強く踏み抜くと…
msgctxt "0004 | c03_225_000 | C000_Saiha"
msgid ""
"Meaning, if you were to apply force to the\n"
"end of the floorboard with no crosspiece..."
msgstr ""

#. 真ん中の横木とカゴの縁が支点となって、
#. テコの要領で茶柱さんの下の床板が跳ね上がるんだ。
msgctxt "0005 | c03_225_000 | C000_Saiha"
msgid ""
"...the next crosspiece would act as a fulcrum\n"
"to turn the floorboard into a lever."
msgstr ""

#. そこに乗っている茶柱さんの体ごとね。
msgctxt "0006 | c03_225_000 | C000_Saiha"
msgid ""
"A lever capable of lifting up\n"
"Tenko's entire body."
msgstr ""

#. 体ごと…跳ね上がる？
msgctxt "0007 | c03_225_000 | C010_Haruk"
msgid "Her whole body...lifted up?"
msgstr ""

#. 確かに、シーソーみてーだけどよ…
#. 茶柱の体を跳ね上げてどうすんだ？
msgctxt "0008 | c03_225_000 | C014_Iruma"
msgid ""
"Yeah, that sounds like a seesaw, alright...\n"
"But why bother lifting Tenko's body?"
msgstr ""

#. それじゃあ、茶柱を殺す事はできねーぞ…
#. あいつを殺した凶器は<CLT=cltSTRONG>カマ<CLT=cltNORMAL>なんだからな。
msgctxt "0009 | c03_225_000 | C001_Momot"
msgid ""
"They couldn't have killed Tenko like \n"
"that...unless they used the <CLT=cltSTRONG>sickle<CLT=cltNORMAL>."
msgstr ""

#. でも、このシーソーの仕掛けを使えば、
#. カゴの中の茶柱さんをカマで殺す事が可能になるんだよ。
msgctxt "0010 | c03_225_000 | C000_Saiha"
msgid ""
"That's exactly it. Using the seesaw trick,\n"
"it was possible to kill Tenko with the sickle."
msgstr ""

#. えっ？　どうやって？
msgctxt "0011 | c03_225_000 | C012_Shiro"
msgid "Huh? How?"
msgstr ""

#. 犯人が茶柱さんを殺す為に、
#. シーソーの仕掛けを利用したとすると…
msgctxt "0012 | c03_225_000 | C000_Saiha"
msgid ""
"In order for the culprit to kill Tenko\n"
"with the seesaw trick..."
msgstr ""

#. 重要なのは…<CLT=cltSTRONG>カマを仕掛けてあった場所<CLT=cltNORMAL>だ。
msgctxt "0013 | c03_225_000 | C000_Saiha"
msgid ""
"...the <CLT=cltSTRONG>placement of the sickle<CLT=cltNORAML> is the\n"
"most important factor."
msgstr ""

#. <CLT=cltMIND>床板のシーソー…
#. そして、カゴの底と白い布に残った血痕…
msgctxt "0014 | c03_225_000 | C000_Saiha"
msgid ""
"<CLT=cltMIND>The floorboard seesaw, the cage,\n"
"and the blood on the white fabric..."
msgstr ""

#. <CLT=cltMIND>そこから導き出される答え…
msgctxt "0015 | c03_225_000 | C000_Saiha"
msgid ""
"<CLT=cltMIND>What conclusions can I\n"
"draw from this?"
msgstr ""

#. <CLT=cltMIND>茶柱さんが殺害された瞬間、
#. 凶器のカマは“あの場所”にあったはずだ。
msgctxt "0016 | c03_225_000 | C000_Saiha"
msgid ""
"<CLT=cltMIND>There's only one place the sickle could\n"
"have been that is consistent with the evidence..."
msgstr ""

#. 鉄カゴのフチ
msgctxt "0017 | c03_225_000 | C000_Saiha"
msgid "Next to the cage"
msgstr ""

#. 凶器のカマは、鉄カゴのフチにあったんだよ。
msgctxt "0018 | c03_225_000 | C000_Saiha"
msgid "The sickle was set up next to the cage."
msgstr ""

#. そこに仕掛けてあって、
#. 茶柱さんを殺す事ってできるのかなぁ…
msgctxt "0019 | c03_225_000 | C012_Shiro"
msgid ""
"Would it really be able to kill\n"
"Tenko if it was placed there?"
msgstr ""

#. しかもフチだと、茶柱さんに気付かれちゃうと思うよ。
msgctxt "0020 | c03_225_000 | C012_Shiro"
msgid ""
"Also, she probably would\n"
"have noticed it there, right?"
msgstr ""

#. <CLT=cltMIND>みんなの冷ややかな視線…
#. 僕の印象が悪くなったみたいだ…
#. <CLT=cltNORMAL>
msgctxt "0021 | c03_225_000 | C000_Saiha"
msgid ""
"<CLT=cltMIND>Everyone's staring at me...\n"
"I screwed up, they think I'm a fraud...\n"
"<CLT=cltNORMAL>"
msgstr ""

#. 床板の裏
msgctxt "0022 | c03_225_000 | C000_Saiha"
msgid "Underneath the floorboard"
msgstr ""

#. 床板の裏にカマを仕掛けて、
#. シーソーの要領でカマが飛び出したんじゃないかな？
msgctxt "0023 | c03_225_000 | C000_Saiha"
msgid ""
"Perhaps the sickle was attached to\n"
"the underside of the floorboard?"
msgstr ""

#. 床板の裏にあったら、
#. いくらシーソーでも飛び出さないんじゃねーか？
msgctxt "0024 | c03_225_000 | C001_Momot"
msgid ""
"Under the floorboard...? The floorboard\n"
"woulda had to flip for it to hit her..."
msgstr ""

#. <CLT=cltMIND>みんなの冷ややかな視線…
#. 僕の印象が悪くなったみたいだ…
#. <CLT=cltNORMAL>
msgctxt "0025 | c03_225_000 | C000_Saiha"
msgid ""
"<CLT=cltMIND>Everyone's staring at me...\n"
"I screwed up, they think I'm a fraud...\n"
"<CLT=cltNORMAL>"
msgstr ""

#. 鉄カゴの底
msgctxt "0026 | c03_225_000 | C000_Saiha"
msgid "The top of the cage"
msgstr ""

#. 被害者と床板の間
msgctxt "0027 | c03_225_000 | C000_Saiha"
msgid "Between the victim and the floorboard"
msgstr ""

#. カマは茶柱さんと床板の間にあったんじゃないかな。
#. シーソーの仕掛けでカマが飛び出した…とか。
msgctxt "0028 | c03_225_000 | C000_Saiha"
msgid ""
"Perhaps the seesaw motion caused the\n"
"sickle to pop up from the floorboard?"
msgstr ""

#. そんなところにあったら
#. 最初に転子が気が付くじゃろ…
msgctxt "0029 | c03_225_000 | C009_Yumen"
msgid ""
"If it was there, Tenko would have\n"
"seen it from the start..."
msgstr ""

#. <CLT=cltMIND>みんなの冷ややかな視線…
#. 僕の印象が悪くなったみたいだ…
#. <CLT=cltNORMAL>
msgctxt "0030 | c03_225_000 | C000_Saiha"
msgid ""
"<CLT=cltMIND>Everyone's staring at me...\n"
"I screwed up, they think I'm a fraud...\n"
"<CLT=cltNORMAL>"
msgstr ""

#. ………………
msgctxt "0031 | c03_225_000 | C000_Saiha"
msgid "..."
msgstr "..."

#. あれ？　どうしたの？
#. 教えてくれるんじゃなかったの？
msgctxt "0032 | c03_225_000 | C012_Shiro"
msgid ""
"Huh? What's wrong?\n"
"Weren't you going to tell us?"
msgstr ""

#. <CLT=cltMIND>みんなの冷ややかな視線…
#. 僕の印象が悪くなったみたいだ…
#. <CLT=cltNORMAL>
msgctxt "0033 | c03_225_000 | C000_Saiha"
msgid ""
"<CLT=cltMIND>Everyone's staring at me...\n"
"I screwed up, they think I'm a fraud...\n"
"<CLT=cltNORMAL>"
msgstr ""

#. <CLT=cltMIND>茶柱さんが殺害された時
#. 凶器のカマがあった場所は…
msgctxt "0034 | c03_225_000 | C000_Saiha"
msgid ""
"<CLT=cltMIND>Where was the sickle when\n"
"Tenko was killed...?"
msgstr ""

#. 凶器のカマを<CLT=cltSTRONG>鉄カゴの底<CLT=cltNORMAL>に仕掛けるんだよ。
#. 刃だけを下に向けた状態でね。
msgctxt "0035 | c03_225_000 | C000_Saiha"
msgid ""
"The sickle was at the top of the <CLT=cltSTRONG>iron cage<CLT=cltNORMAL>,\n"
"with the blade facing down."
msgstr ""

#. しかも、仕掛けたカマは、
#. カゴの上から白い布を被せれば見えなくなってしまう…
msgctxt "0036 | c03_225_000 | C000_Saiha"
msgid ""
"The reason we didn't see it was\n"
"because of the fabric covering the cage."
msgstr ""

#. さらに、その布の上に木像を置く事で、
#. カマは完全に鉄カゴの底に固定されるんだ。
msgctxt "0037 | c03_225_000 | C000_Saiha"
msgid ""
"Also, the wooden statue kept\n"
"the blade in place."
msgstr ""

#. ただ、カマにも厚みがあるから、
#. 乗せた像はほんの少し傾くかもしれないけど…
msgctxt "0038 | c03_225_000 | C000_Saiha"
msgid ""
"It's true that the sickle's handle was thick,\n"
"which made the statue wobble..."
msgstr ""

#. まぁ、あの木像くらいの重さがあれば、
#. 問題なく固定できたはずだよ。
msgctxt "0039 | c03_225_000 | C000_Saiha"
msgid ""
"but the statue's weight kept it\n"
"from falling over."
msgstr ""

#. そして、その状態で、
#. さっきのシーソーの仕掛けを作動させれば…
msgctxt "0040 | c03_225_000 | C000_Saiha"
msgid ""
"Once everything was in place, if you\n"
"stepped hard enough on the seesaw..."
msgstr ""

#. 跳ね上がった茶柱さんの体は、
#. カマの刃が仕掛けられた鉄カゴの底に押し付けられて…
msgctxt "0041 | c03_225_000 | C000_Saiha"
msgid ""
"Tenko's body would have shot upward\n"
"and hit the blade on the top of the cage."
msgstr ""

#. 丸まった体勢の彼女の首筋に、
#. そのカマの刃が突き刺さってしまうんだ。
msgctxt "0042 | c03_225_000 | C000_Saiha"
msgid ""
"She was bent over, meaning the sickle's\n"
"blade would have connected with her neck."
msgstr ""

#. カマの刃は１５センチ程度しかないから、
#. 中の人を刺すにはリーチが足りないって話だったけど…
msgctxt "0043 | c03_225_000 | C010_Haruk"
msgid ""
"The 6-inch sickle blade wasn't long enough \n"
"to stab Tenko in her crouched position."
msgstr ""

#. それを補う為のシーソーの仕掛けなんだね。
msgctxt "0044 | c03_225_000 | C010_Haruk"
msgid ""
"But with the floorboard acting as a seesaw,\n"
"it could compensate for the blade's length."
msgstr ""

#. カマを被害者に近付けるのではなく、
#. 被害者の方をカマに近付けるとは…
msgctxt "0045 | c03_225_000 | C007_Ki-Bo"
msgid ""
"Bringing the victim to the sickle, rather than\n"
"bringing the sickle to the victim..."
msgstr ""

#. まさに、逆転の発想ですね！
msgctxt "0046 | c03_225_000 | C007_Ki-Bo"
msgid "That's definitely an unorthodox idea!"
msgstr ""

#. 突拍子もねー方法だが…
#. それならカゴの中の茶柱をカマで刺す事ができるな…
msgctxt "0047 | c03_225_000 | C001_Momot"
msgid ""
"It's crazy, but it would explain how Tenko \n"
"got stabbed while she was in the cage."
msgstr ""

#. では…ウチらが聞いたあの音は、
#. シーソーにする為に床板を踏み抜いた音だったんじゃな。
msgctxt "0048 | c03_225_000 | C009_Yumen"
msgid ""
"So the sound we heard was the \n"
"culprit stomping on the floorboard."
msgstr ""

#. あの床板はその時の衝撃で外れちゃったんだね。
msgctxt "0049 | c03_225_000 | C004_Gokuh"
msgid "That impact make floorboard come loose."
msgstr ""

#. なるほど！　名付けてシーソー殺人事件か！
msgctxt "0050 | c03_225_000 | C014_Iruma"
msgid ""
"Looks like we got ourselves a good\n"
"ol' fashioned seesaw homicide."
msgstr ""

#. …って、なんだよ、シーソー殺人って！
#. そんなメチャクチャな殺し方ありかよ！
msgctxt "0051 | c03_225_000 | C014_Iruma"
msgid ""
"...Wait, what the hell's a seesaw homicide!?\n"
"That's fucking crazy!"
msgstr ""

#. メチャクチャだからいいんだよ。
#. これはコロシアイゲームなんだよ？
msgctxt "0052 | c03_225_000 | C005_Oma__"
msgid ""
"The craziness is what really makes the\n"
"killing game fun, y'know?"
msgstr ""

#. 逃げ延びる為には、普通の殺し方じゃなくて、
#. 誰もが思い至らない殺し方にしないとね。
msgctxt "0053 | c03_225_000 | C005_Oma__"
msgid ""
"They can't get away with murder the normal\n"
"way, so they gotta think outside the box."
msgstr ""

#. まぁ、そういう意味では犯人も頑張ったよ！
#. つまらなくはないと思うよ！
msgctxt "0054 | c03_225_000 | C005_Oma__"
msgid ""
"Kudos, culprit!\n"
"You did a great job keeping me entertained!"
msgstr ""

#. 本当…夢野さんもやってくれるよネ。
msgctxt "0055 | c03_225_000 | C006_Shing"
msgid "Indeed... Well played, Himiko."
msgstr ""

#. …んあ？
msgctxt "0056 | c03_225_000 | C009_Yumen"
msgid "Nyeeeh?"
msgstr ""

#. ククク…そうなんでしょ？
#. この<CLT=cltSTRONG>“シーソー殺人”<CLT=cltNORMAL>を仕組んだ犯人って君でしょ？
msgctxt "0057 | c03_225_000 | C006_Shing"
msgid ""
"Kehehe... It was you, wasn't it?\n"
"The one behind this <CLT=cltSTRONG>seesaw homicide<CLT=cltNORMAL>?"
msgstr ""

#. えっ！？　なんでそうなるのっ！？
msgctxt "0058 | c03_225_000 | C004_Gokuh"
msgid "Huh!? Why her!?"
msgstr ""

#. この計画を実行できたのが、
#. 彼女しかいないからだヨ…
msgctxt "0059 | c03_225_000 | C006_Shing"
msgid ""
"Because she's the only one capable\n"
"of carrying out this plan..."
msgstr ""

#. 夢野さんしかいないって…どうして？
msgctxt "0060 | c03_225_000 | C012_Shiro"
msgid "The only one? Why's that?"
msgstr ""

#. だって、この“シーソー殺人”を実行するには、
#. 犯人は事前に現場で準備をしておく必要があるんだヨ？
msgctxt "0061 | c03_225_000 | C006_Shing"
msgid ""
"Because this seesaw homicide required\n"
"its location to be prepared beforehand."
msgstr ""

#. 床下の横木を切っておく事ですね？
msgctxt "0062 | c03_225_000 | C007_Ki-Bo"
msgid ""
"By cutting the crosspiece beneath the\n"
"floorboard, you mean?"
msgstr ""

#. その上で、犯人は被害者を
#. その仕掛けがある部屋におびき寄せなければならない…
msgctxt "0063 | c03_225_000 | C006_Shing"
msgid ""
"Then the culprit would need to lure\n"
"their victim into the prepared room."
msgstr ""

#. 夢野さん、君が降霊術をあの部屋でやる事にしたのは、
#. そういう意図があったからなんだよネ？
msgctxt "0064 | c03_225_000 | C006_Shing"
msgid ""
"That is why you chose that room\n"
"for the seance, is it not, Himiko?"
msgstr ""

#. ただ…空き部屋は３つあったよネ？
#. どの部屋にするの？
msgctxt "0065 | c03_225_000 | C006_Shing"
msgid ""
"However...there are three empty rooms.\n"
"Which one shall we use?"
msgstr ""

#. であれば…真ん中じゃな。
#. そういう場合はど真ん中に決まっておる。
msgctxt "0066 | c03_225_000 | C009_Yumen"
msgid ""
"Um...the middle room. The middle \n"
"room's always best for stuff like this."
msgstr ""

#. そう言や、降霊術の場所を決めたのは夢野だったな！
msgctxt "0067 | c03_225_000 | C014_Iruma"
msgid ""
"Oh yeah! Himiko was the one who chose\n"
"the site for the seance!"
msgstr ""

#. ………………
msgctxt "0068 | c03_225_000 | C009_Yumen"
msgid "..."
msgstr "..."

#. きっと、彼女はどこかで、
#. 僕がやろうとしていた降霊術の内容を知ったんだろうネ。
msgctxt "0069 | c03_225_000 | C006_Shing"
msgid ""
"She likely found out about my\n"
"plans for the seance somehow."
msgstr ""

#. あれだけアピールしていた上に、
#. 降霊術の文献も研究教室に置きっ放しでしたからね。
msgctxt "0070 | c03_225_000 | C007_Ki-Bo"
msgid ""
"You were quite vocal about the seance, Kiyo.\n"
"You even had instructions for it in your lab."
msgstr ""

#. そして、この犯行計画を思い付いた夢野さんは
#. 先にシーソーの仕掛けを作っておき…
msgctxt "0071 | c03_225_000 | C006_Shing"
msgid ""
"Our culprit, Himiko, prepared her seesaw trap\n"
"ahead of time..."
msgstr ""

#. 僕が降霊術をやろうと言い出したタイミングで、
#. 迷わず<CLT=cltSTRONG>“真ん中の空き部屋”<CLT=cltNORMAL>を提案したんだ。
msgctxt "0072 | c03_225_000 | C006_Shing"
msgid ""
"Then she waited for me to host the seance, \n"
"and suggested the <CLT=cltSTRONG>middle room<CLT=cltNORMAL>."
msgstr ""

#. そうやって、まんまと
#. あの部屋で降霊術をさせる事に成功した君は…
msgctxt "0073 | c03_225_000 | C006_Shing"
msgid ""
"She led us all into holding the\n"
"seance right where she wanted it."
msgstr ""

#. そこで、計画通りに茶柱さんを殺したんだ。
msgctxt "0074 | c03_225_000 | C006_Shing"
msgid ""
"Then, she killed Tenko.\n"
"All according to plan."
msgstr ""

#. う、嘘でしょ…？
#. そんな事を…夢野さんが？
msgctxt "0075 | c03_225_000 | C012_Shiro"
msgid ""
"Th-That's a lie, right?\n"
"Himiko...did such a thing?"
msgstr ""

#. ………………
msgctxt "0076 | c03_225_000 | C009_Yumen"
msgid "..."
msgstr "..."

#. よりにもよって、茶柱ちゃんが大好きだった夢野ちゃんが、
#. 彼女を殺した犯人とはね…
msgctxt "0077 | c03_225_000 | C005_Oma__"
msgid ""
"In the end, Himiko, who Tenko cherished \n"
"and loved, tragically killed her..."
msgstr ""

#. ちょ、ちょっと待ってよ！
#. まだそう決まった訳じゃないよね！？
msgctxt "0078 | c03_225_000 | C004_Gokuh"
msgid "W-Wait! We don't know that, right!?"
msgstr ""

#. 違うよね、夢野さん！？
#. 夢野さんが茶柱さんを殺すはずないよね！？
msgctxt "0079 | c03_225_000 | C004_Gokuh"
msgid ""
"He's wrong. Right, Himiko!?\n"
"Himiko would never kill Tenko! Right!?"
msgstr ""

#. …転子を…殺す？
msgctxt "0080 | c03_225_000 | C009_Yumen"
msgid "Kill...Tenko...?"
msgstr ""

#. ウチが…転子を殺したじゃと？
msgctxt "0081 | c03_225_000 | C009_Yumen"
msgid "I...killed Tenko?"
msgstr ""

#. ………………
msgctxt "0082 | c03_225_000 | C009_Yumen"
msgid "..."
msgstr "..."

#. 夢野…さん？
msgctxt "0083 | c03_225_000 | C004_Gokuh"
msgid "Himiko...?"
msgstr ""

#. どうしたんですか、夢野さん？
msgctxt "0084 | c03_225_000 | C007_Ki-Bo"
msgid "What's wrong, Himiko?"
msgstr ""

#. ………………
msgctxt "0085 | c03_225_000 | C009_Yumen"
msgid "..."
msgstr "..."

#. <CLT=cltMIND>確かに、シーソーの仕掛けがあった空き部屋に、
#. みんなを誘導したのは夢野さんだったけど…
msgctxt "0086 | c03_225_000 | C000_Saiha"
msgid ""
"<CLT=cltMIND>It is true that using the middle room\n"
"was Himiko's idea..."
msgstr ""

#. <CLT=cltMIND>でも、本当にそうなのか？
#. 夢野さんが茶柱さんを殺したなんて…
msgctxt "0087 | c03_225_000 | C000_Saiha"
msgid ""
"<CLT=cltMIND>But does that mean that\n"
"Himiko really killed Tenko?"
msgstr ""

#. <CLT=cltMIND>そんな事が本当にあるのか？
